| Cache Namespaces | `src/interfaces/cache.interface.ts` | enum Namespaces with 7 predefined values |
| OpenSearch Neural | `src/modules/opensearch/opensearch-neural.service.ts` | Index creation, bulk indexing, text→embedding |
| OpenSearch Service | `src/modules/opensearch/opensearch.service.ts` | ML model management, pipelines, health checks |
| Module Exports | `src/modules/opensearch/opensearch.module.ts` | Exports both services for DI |
| Constants | `src/constants/env-variables.constant.ts` | `OPENSEARCH_MODEL_ID`, TTL constants |
| DTOs | `src/dto/*/` | Query/Response DTOs with full Swagger docs |

